<template>
  <v-card
    color="grey lighten-4"
    flat
    tile
  >
    <v-toolbar>
      <v-toolbar-title>Title</v-toolbar-title>
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>

      <v-btn icon>
        <v-icon>mdi-heart</v-icon>
      </v-btn>

    </v-toolbar>
  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
  name: 'AlbumView',

  components: {
  },

  props: ['id'],

  data() {
    return {
    };
  },
  methods: {
    fetchTracks() {
      axios
        .get('http://127.0.0.1:3000/album')
        .then((response) => {
          this.albums = response.data;
          console.log(this.albums);
        })
        .catch((error) => console.error(error));
    },
  },
  mounted() {
    this.fetchTracks();
  },
};
</script>
